OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA lot of cloud, with patchy
OL,6,Frain for northern and western parts of
OL,7,Fthe UK. The best of the sunshine
OL,8,Freserved for southern and eastern
OL,9,FScotland, but perhaps some brighter
OL,10,Fskies for eastern Northern Ireland and
OL,11,Fsoutheast England at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night to
OL,14,Fcome for most of the country, with
OL,15,Fpatchy rain and drizzle edging
OL,16,Fnorthwards. Turning chilly under any
OL,17,Fclearer breaks, these most likely in
OL,18,FScotland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
