OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMostly cloudy with patchy rain
OL,6,Fdeveloping at times, mainly over
OL,7,Fwestern areas. The cloud may break up
OL,8,Fin the afternoon to allow sunnier
OL,9,Fskies for southeast England and
OL,10,Feastern Scotland.
